         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">27th March 1858. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ With reference to your letter of the 2nd instant, ¶  I have the honor to inform you that the cost of providing the frames for the Botanic Gardens estimated at £68 is prope...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">58.03.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 58/825, unit 1, p. 54, VPRS 975/P2 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">27th March 1858.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to your letter of the 2nd instant,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to D. Moore, 2 March 1858.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to inform you that the cost of providing the frames for the Botanic Gardens estimated at £68 is properly chargeable to the vote for "Tools and apparatus["]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> and that if you think such vote will bear the expense it will be necessary for you to apply to the Honorable the Chief Secretary to cause the necessary authority to issue.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Signed for CPW<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Commissioner of Public Works.</p>
               </note> T. C. Balmain</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of the Botanic Gardens.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
